## 🗃️ Example BigQuery SQL

**CBP (simplified): controlled BP last reading in MY:**
```sql
WITH last_bp AS (
  SELECT
    member_id,
    ARRAY_AGG(STRUCT(bp_systolic, bp_diastolic, measurement_date)
              ORDER BY measurement_date DESC LIMIT 1)[OFFSET(0)] AS last_reading
  FROM `project.dataset.encounters`
  WHERE measurement_date BETWEEN DATE('2025-01-01') AND DATE('2025-12-31')
  GROUP BY member_id
)
SELECT
  member_id,
  (last_reading.bp_systolic < 140 AND last_reading.bp_diastolic < 90) AS controlled_bp
FROM last_bp;
